<h2 style="color: #c9a84c; margin-top: 0;">Registration Not Approved</h2>

<p>Hi {{name}},</p>

<p>
  We regret to inform you that your account registration on the CSE SUST portal
  was <strong style="color: #e74c3c;">not approved</strong>.
</p>

{{#if reason}}
<div class="highlight">
  <p style="margin: 0;">
    <strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}
  </p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p>
  If you believe this was a mistake or would like further clarification, please
  contact the department administration. You may also re-register with corrected
  information if applicable.
</p>

{{#if contactEmail}}
<p>
  You can reach us at:
  <a href="mailto:{{contactEmail}}">{{contactEmail}}</a>
</p>
{{/if}}

<p>
  We appreciate your interest in the CSE SUST community.
</p>

<p>
  Regards,<br />
  <strong style="color: #c9a84c;">CSE SUST Team</strong>
</p>
